originalText.text: I came in last week for pain on the ball of my foot. I didn't have to wait long before being seen by Dr. Mitchell. The office was clean and comfortable. Dr. Mitchell really took his time explaining what was going on with my foot. He was very clear and thorough with his explanations. Dr. Mitchell was also very gentle while examining where the pain was stemming from. Super professional but funny at the same time. I was given many suggestions for home treatments/exercises that really helped nurse my foot. My second visit today, for a follow up, was no different than the first. Very prompt and amazing service. I definitely recommend coming here.
